Evocosm is a set of classes that abstract the fundamental
components of an evolutionary algorithm:

 -- Random Numbers
 -- Validation
 -- Floating- Point Chromosomes
 -- Roulette Wheels
 -- Organisms
 -- Fitness Landscapes
 -- Evocosms
 -- Fitness Scaling
 -- Migration
 -- Selecting Survivors
 -- Reproduction
 -- Mutation Operators

WWW:	http://www.coyotegulch.com/products/libevocosm/index.html
